h1 Who We Are
h2 We are Servants
p.
	In Trees for Life, the focus is on Life.
p.
	We empower the poor to help themselves out of poverty. We focus on the root causes rather than the symptoms. 
p.
	We believe that Information Technology can and should be used to provide the best of training to the elementary school teachers who serve the poor. Suddenly, a very complex and major problem is solvable. 
	
p.
	We work with them to find the “fulcrum” that will give them the leverage to solve their problems rather than become dependent upon others. Thus, we take a long term view in which people can transform the very causes of their problems. 

